  "cigar-news-premium-cigars-win-fight-against-fda": "In a stunning victory, Cigar Association of America, et al v. U.S. Food and Drug Administration ends with the removal of FDA’s regulation over premium cigars. Get the latest news and see how you can continue the fight!",
