  "nowsmoking-foundation-tabernacle-havana-seed-ct-142-cigar-review": "Cigar Advisors Gary Korb and Jared Gulick are #nowsmoking a Lancero for this Tabernacle Havana Seed Connecticut #142 cigar review. Compared to past sizes they’ve smoked from Foundation’s Tabernacle CT #142 line, this new addition provided some illuminating conclusions. Click to see them now!",
