  "ep-carrillo-famous-smoke-shop-80th-anniversary-cigar-review-video": "Next up in the Famous Smoke Shop 80th Anniversary cigar series: the EP Carrillo Famous 80th Anniversary Toro. Among the highlights: a rare hybrid wrapper originally slated for one of Ernesto’s future family blends. Watch now to see if this cigar checked all the right boxes for the reviewers.",
