  "nowsmoking-ep-carrillo-famous-80th-anniversary-cigar-review": "Cigar industry icon Ernesto Perez-Carrillo has created so many high-scoring cigars, they’d be easier to weigh than count. He’s also made the EPC Famous 80th Anniversary, a box pressed Toro with a rare Connecticut hybrid wrapper. Discover what this limited edition cigar has to offer in our #nowsmoking cigar review!",
