  "nowsmoking-black-label-trading-lawless-cigar-review": "After seeing that it received a ’93’ rating in a popular cigar magazine, CigarAdvisor.com executive editor, Gary Korb, teamed-up with Famous Smoke Shop Purchasing Agent, Vilma Ravelo, to see if their #nowsmoking cigar review of the Black Label Trading Company Lawless Churchill actually lived-up to its ‘classic’-designated score. . .",
