  "10-cigars-to-smoke-on-national-cigar-day": "National Cigar Day comes once a year, so no sense wasting it on a cigar that will be forgotten as soon as its snuffed-out. Up the ante for this year’s festivities, with these 10 cigars to smoke on National Cigar Day!",
