  "10-top-toro-cigars-under-10-dollars": "Finding a great cigar and spending a lot is easy. Finding one for less than $10 is another story altogether. We did the research for you and were surprised with the results: lots of brand names and boutiques alike offer big flavor on a reasonable budget. See our top 10 list now!",
