  "dressing-the-cigar-smoker": "When you’re well-dressed, the food tastes better, the drinks feel stronger, and the cigar gives you notes you never knew it had before. Why, you ask? Because when you dress the part you feel better about yourself, and everything you do is enhanced by it. Here are some tips to get you started.",
